text:
Hey everyone, within an email, I am attempting to set multiple fallback properties and i am wondering if anyone has experience doing this.

Here's the snippet that I attempted to use:

```{% if contact.applicant_2_first_name %}
    &lt;p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"&gt;Hello {{ contact.applicant_2_first_name }}&lt;/p&gt;
{% elif contact.applicant_1_first_name %}
    &lt;p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"&gt;Hello {{ contact.applicant_1_first_name }}&lt;/p&gt;
{% elif contact.firstname %}
    &lt;p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"&gt;Hello {{ contact.firstname }}&lt;/p&gt;
{% else %}
    &lt;p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"&gt;Hello there&lt;/p&gt;
{% endif %}```
